  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"content\"\u003e\n\n\u003carticle\u003e\n\n\t\n \t\n \t\n\n \t\n\n \t\n\t\t\n\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eOh how I love this grilled zucchini caesar! Big chunks of zucchini, charred and caramelized on the grill, drizzled with greek yogurt caesar dressing and topped with shaved parmesan and crunchy breadcrumbs. Delicious summer meal!\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eI will turn anything into a caesar! \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003e\u003cimg fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/grilled-zucchini-caesar-9-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"grilled zucchini caesar\" width=\"1790\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/07/grilled-zucchini-caesar/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Grilled Zucchini Caesar.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/grilled-zucchini-caesar-9-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/grilled-zucchini-caesar-9-scaled.jpg 1790w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/grilled-zucchini-caesar-9-728x895.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/grilled-zucchini-caesar-9-768x944.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/grilled-zucchini-caesar-9-1250x1536.jpg 1250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/grilled-zucchini-caesar-9-1666x2048.jpg 1666w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/grilled-zucchini-caesar-9-150x184.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1790px) 100vw, 1790px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201790%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/grilled-zucchini-caesar-9-scaled.jpg 1790w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/grilled-zucchini-caesar-9-728x895.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/grilled-zucchini-caesar-9-768x944.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/grilled-zucchini-caesar-9-1250x1536.jpg 1250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/grilled-zucchini-caesar-9-1666x2048.jpg 1666w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/grilled-zucchini-caesar-9-150x184.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/grilled-zucchini-caesar-9-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis grilled zucchini caesar is incredible. Hearty chunks of zucchini that are grilled until slightly charred, drizzled with my greek yogurt caesar dressing, topped with shaved parmesan and some toasty garlicky sourdough breadcrumbs. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eI LOVE it. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/grilled-zucchini-caesar-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"grilled zucchini caesar\" width=\"1708\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/07/grilled-zucchini-caesar/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Grilled Zucchini Caesar.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/grilled-zucchini-caesar-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/grilled-zucchini-caesar-scaled.jpg 1708w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/grilled-zucchini-caesar-728x938.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/grilled-zucchini-caesar-768x989.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/grilled-zucchini-caesar-1192x1536.jpg 1192w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/gr